    <item>
      <title>The Waiting Room</title>
      <link>https://example.com/stories/the-waiting-room/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Nov 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://example.com/stories/the-waiting-room/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;A short scene demonstrating the theme&amp;rsquo;s theatrical shortcodes.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;stage-direction&#34;&gt;A waiting room. Two plastic chairs. A water cooler that gurgles intermittently. FIONA sits reading a magazine. DECLAN enters, looks around, sits.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;dialogue&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p class=&#34;dialogue-name&#34;&gt;DECLAN&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p class=&#34;dialogue-text&#34;&gt;Is this the right place?&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;dialogue&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p class=&#34;dialogue-name&#34;&gt;FIONA&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p class=&#34;dialogue-text&#34;&gt;Depends what you&amp;rsquo;re waiting for.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;dialogue&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p class=&#34;dialogue-name&#34;&gt;DECLAN &lt;span class=&#34;dialogue-parenthetical&#34;&gt;(hesitantly)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p class=&#34;dialogue-text&#34;&gt;The&amp;hellip; results?&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;dialogue&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p class=&#34;dialogue-name&#34;&gt;FIONA&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p class=&#34;dialogue-text&#34;&gt;Everyone&amp;rsquo;s waiting for results. Sit down.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;stage-direction&#34;&gt;DECLAN sits. The water cooler gurgles. A long silence.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;dialogue&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p class=&#34;dialogue-name&#34;&gt;DECLAN&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p class=&#34;dialogue-text&#34;&gt;How long have you been here?&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;dialogue&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p class=&#34;dialogue-name&#34;&gt;FIONA &lt;span class=&#34;dialogue-parenthetical&#34;&gt;(not looking up)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p class=&#34;dialogue-text&#34;&gt;Hard to say. The clock stopped working on Tuesday.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;dialogue&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p class=&#34;dialogue-name&#34;&gt;DECLAN&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p class=&#34;dialogue-text&#34;&gt;What day is it now?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
